name: jardins
description: jardins is a collection of jardim’s pictures made between March 11th and May 12th 2021. The pictures were created inside jardim/garden/枯山水  simulation by more than 42 people. Between March 11th and April 13th, Taís Koshino visited jardim and created three images daily. After jardim exhibition release (4/21), other people also made their own jardim and shared it. jardim/garden/枯山水 by @TaisKoshino. Code by @koshino & @mutmedia. Available at https://guava.gallery/Jardim. Curated by @mariana9destro.
